```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant W as Web Frontend
    participant A as API Service
    participant P as Platform Service
    participant M as MCP Server
    participant D as Database
    participant S as Storage

    U->>W: Initiate snapshot
    W->>A: POST /api/snapshot
    A->>P: Create snapshot record
    P->>D: Insert snapshot metadata
    D-->>P: Snapshot ID
    P-->>A: Snapshot ID
    A->>M: Request snapshot creation
    M->>S: Store snapshot data
    S-->>M: Storage confirmation
    M->>P: Update snapshot status
    P->>D: Update snapshot record
    D-->>P: Confirmation
    P-->>A: Updated snapshot
    A-->>W: Snapshot details
    W-->>U: Display snapshot confirmation
```